            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Poor onboarding, mismatched sales expectations, insufficient ongoing value, competitive alternatives, and acquiring bad-fit customers. Product bugs and pricing changes drive spikes. The single largest lever is usually first-week product activation.</p></div></div>
